{"tid":1784980,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黃店 = 官方page出post同喺店入面貼反警暴撐示威者相關標語","createTime":"2019-12-16T05:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T06:02:29.000Z","uid":5866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fd32af505f94601be8964971ca9f85313254de6a","tid":1784980,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:11:29.000Z","msg":"記住，你幫襯錯一間偽黃就等於幫襯少咗一間真黃店<br />\n<br />\n今次擺明大J阿哥怕大陸生意受影響，自己唔出post叫大J出post<br />\n噉有起事上嚟就話大J不代表我，冇事就可以食盡兩家茶禮。<br />\n<br />\n點防止？好簡單<br />\n無論如何，相關店鋪都應該喺<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">官方</span></span>嘅page出post反警暴撐示威者<br />\n再喺間鋪入面嘅當眼位貼最少一張反警暴撐示威者嘅紙<br />\n然後就一律當黃店處理<br />\n<br />\n如果出個post貼張紙都做唔到你黃咩店呢？想叫外人做等你有走盞位食盡兩家茶禮？"},{"pid":"dcde1f106477f64ebe0b037b3b436010f885c8cd","tid":1784980,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:12:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽晚7點愛丁堡見</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">哀悼香港人道災難</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PY03AQa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPY03AQa.jpg&h=511bc04b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12ae90ea361f4255c1f67cda9b7a43326f433b8e","tid":1784980,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:13:44.000Z","msg":"門檻低又冇藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307d0ee486544c1f7fe0bc96bbd145d48e6ae08f","tid":1784980,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e662d8888d07cb5f28b477ee38f7b56adc844851","tid":1784980,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T06:02:29.000Z","msg":"班 狗 最 怕 我 哋 咁 做<br />\n<a hr